Incorrect calculations. For example squaring a negative gives a negative in return (-8^2 --> -64) everything else is good
replyContent:
Dear Sebastian,

it's normal on Ti 84 and other famous Calculator. It's because (-) operator plays lower priority than ^ operator. So, Please put the number into (...) E.g: (-8)^2 -> 64.

Regards, PM
